      <title>療癒日記｜親愛的，我得到了人生中第一個遺憾。</title>
      <link>https://niyou0509.github.io/blog/2024.11.05%E7%99%82%E7%99%92%E6%97%A5%E8%A8%98%E8%A6%AA%E6%84%9B%E7%9A%84%E6%88%91%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE/</link>
